        "details": {
            "casino": {
                "badge": "100% MATCH BONUS",
                "title": "Live Casino First Deposit Bonus",
                "intro": "Experience the thrill of real casino gaming with professional dealers and authentic table games, enhanced by a generous 100% match bonus on your first deposit.",
                "prose1": "The 100% Live Casino First Deposit Bonus is specifically designed for new players who appreciate the authentic casino experience with real human dealers streaming live from professional casino studios. This bonus gives you a fantastic opportunity to explore premium live casino games without risking too much of your own money. When you make your first deposit, BIGWIN959 matches it 100%, effectively doubling your starting bankroll and giving you twice the playing time to learn the games, develop strategies, and potentially win big.",
                "prose2": "Live casino gaming offers a unique experience that combines the convenience of online play with the authenticity and social interaction of land-based casinos. You'll see real cards being dealt, real roulette wheels spinning, and real dice being rolled — all in high-definition video quality with multiple camera angles. Professional dealers interact with players through live chat, creating an immersive and engaging atmosphere that slot machines and RNG games simply cannot replicate. This bonus is your gateway to experiencing this premium gaming format with enhanced bankroll protection.",
                "gamesTitle": "What Games Are Included?",
                "gamesIntro": "This bonus is valid for all live casino games from premium providers including Evolution Gaming, Sexy Gaming, SA Gaming, and other top-tier live dealer platforms. The most popular games include:",
