                "whyTitle": "Why Choose Live Casino Bonus?",
                "whyIntro": "Live casino gaming offers several advantages that make this bonus particularly valuable for new players:",
                "whyPoints": [
                    "Transparency and Trust: Watch every card dealt and every wheel spin in real-time. No RNG algorithms — just pure, verifiable randomness you can see with your own eyes.",
                    "Social Interaction: Chat with professional dealers and other players. The social element makes gaming more enjoyable and less isolating than playing alone.",
                    "Authentic Experience: Recreates the atmosphere of prestigious land-based casinos from the comfort of your home. Professional studios with elegant decor and attractive dealers.",
                    "Skill Development: Games like Blackjack and Baccarat allow you to develop and apply strategies. The bonus gives you extra funds to practice and improve your skills.",
