            "cricket": {
                "badge": "BIGWIN959 EXCLUSIVE",
                "title": "125% Cricket First Deposit Bonus",
                "intro": "The only 125% cricket betting bonus in the industry — exclusively available at BIGWIN959. Designed for cricket enthusiasts who want maximum value.",
                "exclusiveTitle": "Why This Bonus is Exclusive to BIGWIN959",
                "exclusiveProse1": "The 125% Cricket First Deposit Bonus is a groundbreaking offer that you won't find anywhere else in the online betting industry. While most platforms offer standard 50-100% bonuses for sports betting, BIGWIN959 recognizes the massive passion for cricket in Bangladesh and Myanmar and has created this exclusive 125% bonus specifically for cricket betting. This isn't just a marketing gimmick — it's a genuine commitment to providing the best value for cricket fans who form the core of the platform's user base.",
                "exclusiveProse2": "This exclusive bonus demonstrates BIGWIN959's understanding of the cricket betting market and its dedication to serving cricket enthusiasts better than any competitor. The platform has invested heavily in cricket coverage, offering comprehensive markets for every major tournament and match, and this bonus is the cherry on top — giving new players an unmatched 125% boost to start their cricket betting journey. No other platform offers this level of generosity for cricket betting, making BIGWIN959 the clear choice for serious cricket bettors.",
                "timingTitle": "Perfect Timing for New Cricket Bettors",
                "timingProse1": "If you're new to cricket betting, there has never been a better time to start than now with this exclusive 125% bonus. Cricket betting can seem complex at first with its various markets like match winner, top batsman, session betting, and over/under totals, but this generous bonus gives you extra cushion to learn the ropes without depleting your bankroll too quickly. The additional 25% compared to standard 100% bonuses means you have significantly more funds to experiment with different betting strategies, understand how odds work, and discover which markets suit your knowledge and prediction style best.",
                "timingProse2": "New players often make mistakes as they learn — betting on unfavorable odds, misunderstanding market rules, or misjudging match conditions. With a 125% bonus, these learning experiences don't hurt as much because you're playing with a larger bonus cushion. By the time you've worked through the wagering requirements, you'll have gained valuable experience across multiple matches and tournaments, developed a better understanding of cricket betting dynamics, and potentially built a nice profit from your enhanced starting bankroll. This bonus essentially pays you to learn cricket betting, which is an incredible opportunity for newcomers.",
                "coverageTitle": "Comprehensive Cricket Coverage",
                "coverageIntro": "This bonus is valid for all cricket betting markets across all tournaments and matches covered by BIGWIN959's multiple sports betting providers (SBO Sports, IBC Sports, BTI Sports, Exchange Sports). The coverage includes:",
