                "subtitle": "Ancient Chinese Dice Game",
                "overview": {
                    "title": "Game Overview",
                    "p1": "Sic Bo (骰寶), meaning 'precious dice' or 'dice pair,' is an ancient Chinese gambling game that has been played for centuries. The game uses three dice and offers a wide variety of betting options, from simple even-money bets to high-risk, high-reward wagers with massive payouts.",
                    "p2": "Live Sic Bo brings this traditional game to life with professional dealers shaking the dice in a transparent chest or cage. The game's combination of simplicity and variety makes it appealing to both casual players and serious gamblers."
